text: Masevaux-Niederbruck is a new commune of the Haut-Rhin department of eastern France. It was incorporated on 1 January 2016 by the combination of the former communes of Masevaux and Niederbruck.Arrêté 22 December 2015 == References == Category:Communes in Haut-Rhin Category:2016 establishments in France
title: Masevaux-Niederbruck
